---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'April 3, 2026';
---

<Layout
  title="Accessibility Statement | Alma"
  description="Alma Studio's accessibility statement, including accessibility contact details and the adjustments made across the website."
>
  <Navbar />

  <main id="main-content" tabindex="-1" class="pt-28 pb-20 px-6 md:px-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <header class="mb-12 border-b border-black/10 pb-8">
        <p class="text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-stone-600 mb-4">Accessibility Statement</p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl mb-6">Accessibility Statement</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-stone-800">
          Alma Studio works to provide a respectful, clear, and comfortable browsing experience for all visitors,
          including people with disabilities.
        </p>
      </header>

      <section class="space-y-6 mb-12" aria-labelledby="legal-basis">
        <h2 id="legal-basis" class="text-2xl md:text-3xl">Accessibility framework</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-stone-800">
          This website has been updated in line with accessibility principles commonly applied in Israel,
          including the Equal Rights for Persons with Disabilities Regulations (Accessibility Adjustments to
          Service), 2013, and Israeli Standard 5568, which is based on WCAG 2.0 Level AA.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-stone-800">
          Because websites are dynamic environments, some areas may still require ongoing review or further
          refinement. If you encounter any difficulty, we would appreciate hearing from you so we can address it
          promptly.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-6 mb-12" aria-labelledby="site-adjustments">
        <h2 id="site-adjustments" class="text-2xl md:text-3xl">Accessibility adjustments made on the site</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-3 text-lg text-stone-800">
          <li>Added a “Skip to main content” link for faster keyboard navigation.</li>
          <li>Improved the primary and mobile navigation with support for Tab, Escape, and open/close states.</li>
          <li>Strengthened focus visibility for links, buttons, and form fields.</li>
          <li>Improved text contrast in key areas of the site.</li>
          <li>Added alternative text for content images and marked decorative images appropriately.</li>
          <li>Added clear form labels instead of relying on placeholders alone.</li>
          <li>Adjusted animations and motion behavior for users who prefer reduced motion.</li>
          <li>Used a clear semantic structure for headings, content regions, forms, and navigation.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-6 mb-12" aria-labelledby="widget-info">
        <h2 id="widget-info" class="text-2xl md:text-3xl">Accessibility helper widget</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-stone-800">
          The site includes an accessibility helper widget that offers actions such as display adjustments and
          reading support. This tool is intended to assist users, but it does not replace accessibility built into
          the site’s code and does not, by itself, constitute legal compliance.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-6 mb-12" aria-labelledby="compatibility">
        <h2 id="compatibility" class="text-2xl md:text-3xl">Compatibility and use</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-stone-800">
          The website was built to support keyboard navigation, left-to-right browsing in English, and use in
          common modern browsers on desktop and mobile devices.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-6 mb-12" aria-labelledby="accessibility-contact">
        <h2 id="accessibility-contact" class="text-2xl md:text-3xl">Accessibility contact</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-stone-800">
          If you encounter an issue, find content that is not accessible to you, or need further assistance, please
          contact us and we will do our best to provide an appropriate response as soon as possible.
        </p>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-black/10 p-6 space-y-3 text-lg text-stone-800">
          <p>
            Email:
            <a href="mailto:chani@alma-architects.com" class="underline" dir="ltr">chani@alma-architects.com</a>
          </p>
          <p>
            Phone:
            <a href="tel:+972543395560" class="underline" dir="ltr">054-339-5560</a>
          </p>
          <p>Address: 10 Yonatan St., Neve Shamir, Beit Shemesh</p>
          <p>Statement last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
